    "Each of these platforms offers a different set of student's features, such as demographic, previous, and current academic performance and learning behavioral/activity features.",
    "Examples of universities that have been used in the reviewed research include the International University of La Rioja, Bangladesh University, Shenyang University, Anhui University, Bharathiar University, Beijing University, Gadjah Mada University, Institute of Science, Trade Technology (ISTT), Bina Nusantara University, Hellenic Open University, and National Taipei University of Technology (NTUT), etc.",
    "The studies that use LMSs dataset are Aljaloud et al (2022 Furthermore, other datasets collected from different platforms and used to capture patterns from student's data include the following:",
    "• The UCI Machine Learning library which is a library of datasets that is open to the public and used in DL studies for developing student's academic performance predictive models.",
    "There are more than 400 datasets in the repository that cover a wide range of subjects, however, only the datasets for Mathematics and Portuguese language courses were used in the reviewed studies."
